  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>싸바리 박스 소량 생산은</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-df2f0296-1eea-448e-b477-48508efbbb98\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fd22d59a-f1a6-4361-b6a5-281636da6e30\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ee5f0854-31e1-4c90-88ce-f73372ed707a\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">결론 먼저</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9e0ba7f0-8f39-4987-a034-650c474bd4dc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7429d04a-b87a-4e7f-90ab-d143f527222f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-794a566f-e78d-4efb-b84a-027332d014bb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">싸바리 박스 소량 생산은 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-578c4aee-b383-4fad-94e4-1a8883969fb9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-68bbb0b6-9731-4cf5-b0c1-0b364fe989e3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">다만 @개당 단가와 납기를 확인하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6949ef51-bd5c-4515-9431-75cce09e9e51\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-74da1ae9-7b6b-496f-ae58-d86af93f78b2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0fecbe8f-8273-40de-9494-82803c241f94\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d7b43c12-6cff-4d22-95a2-e83026da1019\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">샘플 2개 생산도 가능하지만 개당 단가는 매우 높습니다. 그리고 100개 생산과 500개 생산의 단가가 차이가 거의 없을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-32c43983-c809-461d-8f47-41f46c42e90b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9f130591-3751-4d02-af72-4349c1d7f039\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-60107981-89ea-4ecf-9bbc-8acd5e6686d4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-60107981-89ea-4ecf-9bbc-8acd5e6686d4\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMTAy/MDAxNzU3ODEzODMxNzEw.PNAt2C0jYhplNl7vIR0z4aR2pNAdY4U4VOTd9C5knxkg.TPFNRbGMoA5DYUphLyqtlOGEKn3YezSmB3h-9mfV7Jkg.PNG/%EC%8B%B8%EB%B0%94%EB%A6%AC_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8001.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1785\", \"originalHeight\" : \"680\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMTAy/MDAxNzU3ODEzODMxNzEw.PNAt2C0jYhplNl7vIR0z4aR2pNAdY4U4VOTd9C5knxkg.TPFNRbGMoA5DYUphLyqtlOGEKn3YezSmB3h-9mfV7Jkg.PNG/%EC%8B%B8%EB%B0%94%EB%A6%AC_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8001.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">싸바리 박스</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">박스 중에 싸바리 박스는 가장 비싼 박스 유형 중에 하나입니다. 물론 사양에 따라서 다르겠지만 가장 고급스럽고 튼튼하며 모든 후공정으로 멋을 낼 수도 있고 제품보호용으로도 탁월한 성능을 자랑합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f29f7157-9769-4ae0-aeab-b3081f8706bb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-64127935-8410-4e23-b537-e2860f3b481b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d2c8e1d8-2a1a-4bab-93be-145c4aeee172\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a983a3c9-72ea-4d4c-ab3f-5f06a376a8f8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 이 외의 형태에서 슬리브 형태나 커스텀 형태로 독자적인 모양을 만들기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a8430543-53b4-45f6-8a73-fd16bb138a9f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a8430543-53b4-45f6-8a73-fd16bb138a9f\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMTYw/MDAxNzU3ODE0MTU2NjE0.VKMMQhRON6wOIkAEH3kitc23H3DlLimOE6YdDVExJUwg.3lrEi_uh_1v6UHVetJv3ggQLB0xjNcpzkINeP1bWsWcg.PNG/%EC%8A%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%8C_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8001.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMTYw/MDAxNzU3ODE0MTU2NjE0.VKMMQhRON6wOIkAEH3kitc23H3DlLimOE6YdDVExJUwg.3lrEi_uh_1v6UHVetJv3ggQLB0xjNcpzkINeP1bWsWcg.PNG/%EC%8A%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%8C_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8001.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5ba4b55b-1908-44bb-b942-0edb995afd95\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ab99486-ba6d-4755-87a7-4cacdeeabbf1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a40f90bc-635d-4bdd-be15-1d328ec2196e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사이즈나 형태에 따라서 다르지만 일반적으로 단가는 다음과 같이 책정됩니다. 물론 비교 사양은 동일 종이와 동일 사이즈일 때의 단순 비교입니다. 그러므로 절대적이지 않고 참고만 하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-16296631-5ec4-4d85-80d5-99ec3a0401af\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-16296631-5ec4-4d85-80d5-99ec3a0401af\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMTY1/MDAxNzU3ODIwMjQxMjQ2.l9vM8Fjo2_BZqD7CSSfbWeW4jSpdrosULVJcA5lTCNEg.46MFYJDaL8VUq7dh8RXlqHvzfGhUwSgfI7b7hHyBUzUg.PNG/%EC%8A%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%8C_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8002.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMTY1/MDAxNzU3ODIwMjQxMjQ2.l9vM8Fjo2_BZqD7CSSfbWeW4jSpdrosULVJcA5lTCNEg.46MFYJDaL8VUq7dh8RXlqHvzfGhUwSgfI7b7hHyBUzUg.PNG/%EC%8A%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%8C_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8002.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-65780962-e463-4c21-9916-978d013f1613\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ffe9a251-ba77-4587-a8fd-194e0c822008\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0630cff8-9db3-45b6-bcf0-93a96f31f8ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a8a5b3d3-884a-436f-8c68-a8683a70e861\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7e7d43d1-aebf-404e-bed8-2298a837f9c6\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>단가</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-964611d2-3ba7-4fe4-af9d-4e98731df44f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ae084ab3-0e93-4b13-b006-c7ffe5e4df93\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">슬리브/커스텀 형태 &gt; 표지 자석 싸바리 박스 &gt; 3단 싸바리 박스 &gt; 2단 싸바리 박스</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b0069870-a913-4e13-b372-24e269da8c1a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-41d35675-b847-4c51-9f5a-63e740e157b4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-10c35a43-ca05-4f27-a7ee-6bb544a79c98\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cd3b197c-ec8e-44cf-b5bb-3daee5efeaf3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">의 순서입니다. 참고만 하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f60f30a1-98e1-4855-b024-edf8538428c2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-17e68fe1-2d1a-4699-a5dd-235848870b68\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dc012af2-62a8-4986-a131-b0f322ff02f1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-016ff31a-059f-492c-965b-8949033e4df8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 이유로 납기나 제작 기간도 위 순서와 동일합니다. 커스텀은 독자적으로 모양을 연구 개발하여 만들기 때문에 수작업으로 진행될 가능성이 많아 단가나 납기가 비싸질 수밖에 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-17b40970-a186-42e0-8fe0-29b592d9d0fe\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e308fe97-a0ea-4c9b-8c70-3e58257e0303\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f31d1288-87ad-4457-a900-972d37fc3b18\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-928913c1-8b95-470a-8ca2-863badc12424\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그렇다면 이런 싸바리 박스의 소량 생산에서의 수량 기준은 어떻게 될까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eee6e30c-7576-414b-b099-6f53b074fab9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0deff1af-f17d-46dc-891b-23be60d50401\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c551561c-563b-400e-9631-d931e1a8570f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-38a7fb0f-39e6-440d-82dc-84efcc7dc268\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객 여러분이 싸바리 제작회사에 문의하실 때 반드시 사전에 고민하고 요청해야 할 부분 중에 하나가 수량일 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d1e3926f-c992-4842-841c-48cc56f22da3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-418ba0a1-2ddd-4209-8441-5bb15c3cdfdc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ce8031a1-e3db-4d5f-9b09-b5e9c5ea713e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-40b25d2d-9dab-4f08-9260-c2d605effa87\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">통상적으로는 싸바리 박스의 소량 생산은 불가능(?) 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d4077a0c-2080-43ad-9366-7708286cb5e4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c355284c-4757-433d-95d8-4015d0bf7768\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-982db60b-e9f7-4135-aec9-1eb05bef305f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-49d6e464-d4eb-4258-8d0f-aa4536878859\" style=\"color:#555555;\">불가능하다기보다는 가능하더라도 단가 때문에 포기하는 경우가 거의 대부분입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5752d8cb-a37c-46ce-9922-0c6284271cae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c13f5595-8e67-47f4-a72e-8375bde7f26e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-986ee579-f961-4df1-9fc5-73888d41f5d4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-49ff6873-1cf7-4d7a-bcc6-870a3717bb25\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자석 싸바리 박스를 20개만 생산하고 싶다는 문의가 많습니다. 그렇다면 다음 사이즈 표지 자석 싸바리 박스의 20개 제작 금액은 어떻게 될까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-181b922e-2e7d-4a5a-9b95-f4ad24a95b88\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7d3b5aa7-b41f-41e8-9f31-767ef4d712dc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e71c2fda-e5aa-46df-8e68-9e7a907b7202\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4de9d677-57d2-4c24-bd5c-07d66f4a94af\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e4fcadd6-3887-4241-8b77-c62457b2a55f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 일반 편아트지 사용</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-935f1dc0-fb36-4195-8199-cf531ef681d4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-91b9a664-de00-44b0-8d3e-50f1093cc116\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>갱판지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4b783e5a-7fb8-440a-b5b0-048d57e7a6a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 일반 1000DDT</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9983457c-4dc2-4c7e-8625-d357f261358e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-91c548e9-7353-41e5-a134-c905edd79101\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-735238e9-be76-4b1f-b498-004b77f4bd1d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 200mm×200mm×100mm</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f3762c87-5a68-4dac-bc6a-4ff103f93413\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-73bad596-c75d-4449-a036-0973223e0a9d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-87ee654e-5cdf-43b9-bb15-f72c6917aa5e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 일반 CMYK 컬러 인쇄</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5edb9037-9d7d-4f7f-9d81-4e2fbf636975\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-03c5bde3-77b4-4036-8102-fa16ad5c8cdf\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>외부</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c55d1a5-cffe-4fa8-aeca-e0eed3fee3ee\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 단면 코팅</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fb0379cd-60a6-4613-89f3-b8a1cab2c7d0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0c82445a-7872-4a37-a74a-959c4864c4b1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이 패드</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8ca70bd6-7eaf-417e-9af1-8d815c12db21\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 없음</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-164221a2-97ed-42e1-95ea-1ff104debf46\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f0b0a47e-f42b-4e17-b3db-8ff8ec77d1fa\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0ce97313-8687-4826-a249-6b338d0c38e8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 없음</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-53f8af7b-88e3-4a97-a6c8-9e92fef0c279\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-81cb6118-911b-462a-a6c2-e4365d48981a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-94910307-2e20-4972-8b83-bcbbbc3f2afd\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 20개</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-acc68e7a-c366-4380-a939-0f3c16ca7ee9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-acc68e7a-c366-4380-a939-0f3c16ca7ee9\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMjgw/MDAxNzU3ODE1MDE5NTU5.-CPtNEqRQ9ZKRoBnzhJlo6Y_Uww0uxD4OZRl07cQllgg.u-aGTv-i14gW_ETTbOQnn4tex-EzFdzY15SQ_VDEfTwg.PNG/%EC%8B%B8%EB%B0%94%EB%A6%AC_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8002.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMjgw/MDAxNzU3ODE1MDE5NTU5.-CPtNEqRQ9ZKRoBnzhJlo6Y_Uww0uxD4OZRl07cQllgg.u-aGTv-i14gW_ETTbOQnn4tex-EzFdzY15SQ_VDEfTwg.PNG/%EC%8B%B8%EB%B0%94%EB%A6%AC_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8002.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ab93e99b-72cc-4703-8922-745a98c4efd4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-34d0c94a-465c-4c40-9764-5670c160afcf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-133d4cc4-6393-4e2b-8c4a-58abf974a468\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객 여러분이 위 사양과 같은 자석 싸바리 박스가 필요하시다면 얼마의 단가라면 제작할 용의가 있으실까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22b88a7a-5c2c-4563-a1bb-ccc0c8b1beba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f78fe860-a542-4344-9482-5ba8099c97c4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c6f2f9dc-ae1d-4b87-9823-187b8b2a6b6a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-88a07860-3b76-48fd-828a-8c545444b1b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">정답은 없지만 일단 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7764d10a-0aca-4aa7-9d94-f369b09950ce\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>무조건 100만 원 미만으로는 제작이 불가능</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2ccc397c-884b-46bd-bce1-390a3fc2df96\" style=\"color:#555555;\">할 겁니다. 최소한 저희 회사는 그렇습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-968831b1-07cc-4f01-ac1a-183b36e6da88\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-07e74356-bd19-42b5-8aaf-f81ea70c0f8e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ea322d30-361a-4880-b868-d3cf7d23e877\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-19953f55-5738-4605-9c5d-85ee61a2c966\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만약 20개 만드는데 100만 원이면 하나에 @개당 5만 원이 넘는 금액으로 제작하시는 겁니다. 이런 이유로 견적을 물어 보고 거의 대부분 포기하시는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ab1c4ea-c24d-45d3-b41e-30aaed954646\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-602215c9-1bbc-4f10-8522-35f8b105c4f2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b1ff9ffb-b1d0-4871-9080-3b2dedbbb6b9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-da955ccc-e58f-4cf7-a05f-378b86541955\" style=\"color:#555555;\">요즘은 스타일러나 디지털 커팅 기계의 발달로 인해 소량 생산 위주의 패키지 업체가 늘어나고 있는 추세이기는 하지만 기본적으로 표지 싸바리 박스의 경우에는 소량으로 제작이 거의 불가능하고 전개도 사이즈가 크다면 인쇄 또한 디지털 인디고 기계로 되지 않기 때문에 소량 생산은 어려움이 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3726744d-c5e1-4234-b59e-c31d37637530\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f4afbaa3-defa-4969-93cc-f0c8eb092bc8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-677ef1d5-50fa-4af1-a8b0-47caa4c4af2a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dcf425ac-615e-4a93-bbe7-9e5691c08510\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 상세페이지 촬영, 방송용 소품 제작, 기타 VIP 한정품 생산의 요청에 의해 대량으로 제작이 의미 없다고 말씀하시는 고객님이 늘어남에 따라 (주)파파스컴퍼니도 소량 생산의 경쟁력을 점점 높여가고 있는 중입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eaf6dd78-8e7f-4926-a77b-28f8c9e5588a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-be8d8447-0283-42c5-b582-03faff7974c3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ca96ca17-824f-4b19-9447-72ddb50661ea\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c2e65655-98eb-44e3-947a-f742e9df237e\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>절대 소량 생산이 안 되는 것</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a883c62e-048b-416c-b775-1bf33e4a0c97\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9f95b23f-8582-4512-8874-124ebd72602a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4ef94e02-9492-48f2-90c8-21280b0254d1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b8c5a694-0522-4415-b331-63f52700d1cf\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 사이즈가 커서 쪽바리(이어 붙이기)나 하드롱으로만 제작이 되는 경우</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f3775819-a242-43c1-a567-5acad11584fc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-57333b21-241b-4699-a2ff-186f6608c88f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-23568eef-d429-47a6-947d-bfcf71c9098a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3166bf8e-1a75-46f7-89f4-4881a93375cd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">한쪽 면이 보통 400mm가 넘으면 일단 소량 생산은 안된다고 보시기 바랍니다. 이런 사이즈는 수작업으로 제작이 되고 소량 생산이 된다고 하더라도 단가가 무척 비싸질 수밖에 없습니다. 그래서 견적을 알려드리면 대부분 제작 포기를 하십니다. 어쩌면 당연할 수 있습니다. @개당 단가가 몇십만 원까지 한다면 제작할 수 없기 때문입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ab9482e8-b14b-4c8c-af67-9fa1dd13d61d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-ab9482e8-b14b-4c8c-af67-9fa1dd13d61d\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMTU2/MDAxNzU3ODIwMTExOTE4.k2KIzdkO-f-UGwgJtvdWRydqOOjmdAXhz4S-2Jvoqjwg.RrKuPtLySbnhSCynNdK5BDezRIczAiFArBgG8e9JxF4g.PNG/%EC%8B%B8%EB%B0%94%EB%A6%AC_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8003.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMTU2/MDAxNzU3ODIwMTExOTE4.k2KIzdkO-f-UGwgJtvdWRydqOOjmdAXhz4S-2Jvoqjwg.RrKuPtLySbnhSCynNdK5BDezRIczAiFArBgG8e9JxF4g.PNG/%EC%8B%B8%EB%B0%94%EB%A6%AC_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8003.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cd2ec52c-587f-44b0-9b18-fdf524023c28\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-cd2ec52c-587f-44b0-9b18-fdf524023c28\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTVfMTEg/MDAxNzU3ODk1MzA2MTIx.gvnf3ij0pf0Lyjw-s0wplqQNBL2oWtnxZhb8607oM2Ig.UfGgG4ouJ_jyKcpsOYK5X3lMtDbv1dNpRmCclqx3tKEg.JPEG/KakaoTalk_20250823_121644677_08.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"4000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTVfMTEg/MDAxNzU3ODk1MzA2MTIx.gvnf3ij0pf0Lyjw-s0wplqQNBL2oWtnxZhb8607oM2Ig.UfGgG4ouJ_jyKcpsOYK5X3lMtDbv1dNpRmCclqx3tKEg.JPEG/KakaoTalk_20250823_121644677_08.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-00befaa6-84c6-45b0-ad2f-3ff49cca0941\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b73e43dc-8a10-4f41-8db8-555365347f1d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e999b993-0a34-4c40-8f2b-41f3234b7d52\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 복잡한 후공정이 있는 경우</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6d653ff8-91f7-4022-b712-06553342059c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-db18ed50-3fad-47f6-b153-31198fe6509f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8683f3b7-34d5-46c6-bf71-8f765103dd8e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6da060d6-fae2-49a0-8da2-ca66a06c5fde\" style=\"color:#555555;\">예를 들어 박인쇄만 해도 동판비나 아연판비가 들어가기 때문에 후공정이 있는 샘플 소량 생산을 원하실 경우는 단가가 비싸질 수밖에 없습니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7b29c1d1-dabb-472b-a3c7-7a2e6abba58b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">물론 대량 주문을 근거로 샘플을 제작하기 위한 소량 생산이라면 나중에 동판비나 목형비를 제외해 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d646e186-e2e7-4e9a-9eca-816f75fa5eec\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-16de6680-f23f-4a72-9026-3f03022c983c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e4c3f0de-2600-45d8-802c-3f105655d615\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c9c34b16-7994-4ba0-9b6f-9b5a9a78c027\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그렇다고 하도라도 일단 샘플 제작비용이 무척 비싸질 수밖에 없습니다. 고객의 입장에서는 샘플을 보고 본 작업 대량 생산을 원하시기도 하지만 그건 샘플 제작비용의 투자가 이루어졌을 때만 가능한 이야기입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bb554d1e-94f4-4c0a-9447-5098be09f4d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-bb554d1e-94f4-4c0a-9447-5098be09f4d5\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMTg4/MDAxNzU3ODIwMTA0MDE4.HoHFI7_Ge1ccl5sTamFI8HjyauTOaIHRvghnI2fQmzog.JLihgwQWGfVFmWNPWF6nDTlEFhfbesAYNot06v7P-rkg.PNG/%EC%8B%B8%EB%B0%94%EB%A6%AC_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8005.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMTg4/MDAxNzU3ODIwMTA0MDE4.HoHFI7_Ge1ccl5sTamFI8HjyauTOaIHRvghnI2fQmzog.JLihgwQWGfVFmWNPWF6nDTlEFhfbesAYNot06v7P-rkg.PNG/%EC%8B%B8%EB%B0%94%EB%A6%AC_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8005.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a7dfc485-a79d-4e7d-8f79-4aade5bb9b71\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d0811eef-414e-4587-bc8f-ba344246b65a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fb23b512-f998-4f1d-9f28-deba96e902bc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c9c16502-8a19-4617-8960-000b9e1a9949\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-75d1c1b6-2a26-4594-a5f7-aeb3e5dc623c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 납기를 2~4일로 생각하시는 고객님</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-03bc5170-0c8c-48a6-86f5-477e608afd18\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8b2825ac-f98a-423f-bde8-b90dd65a526f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d903deb2-7c6e-4ec1-84be-9f2735a14025\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9ee97824-25dc-409d-8156-3dacbc8daab6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">샘플도 일반 본 작업처럼 많은 부분의 작업이 선행돼야 합니다. 목형도 만들고 디자인 데이터 컨펌도 해야 하므로 본 작업만큼은 아니더라도 시간 소요가 발생합니다. 물론 5일 이내 작업도 할 수 있지만 그건 완전 소양의 경우입니다. 특히 내부 패드 작업까지라면 일정은 더 소요됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a40f3cff-dad3-4a79-bb28-5537c4b00bf6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-af4268bd-3cb8-4220-8feb-a9895a733902\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0c88113c-8245-415c-8ee3-b8d1dddc58c1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0ffba77f-4afd-4ccf-bd2b-118920def2f4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">최소 5일에서 최장 10일 이상 소요될 수 있습니다. 이건 후공정이나 사이즈에 영향을 받습니다. 참고해 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6301fd3e-a1f9-4ab9-9ed2-f08d9bf5f247\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6301fd3e-a1f9-4ab9-9ed2-f08d9bf5f247\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMSAg/MDAxNzU3ODIwMDk1MTg0.ozV6lCu57xpCgps8jTJuNKOcWE3iJxmDNBVH0-nnzXog.8s-4_87nfQ6JzT8vnx6VM4d_ecFHeAey6dSDKWjlYSkg.PNG/%EC%8B%B8%EB%B0%94%EB%A6%AC_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8004.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA5MTRfMSAg/MDAxNzU3ODIwMDk1MTg0.ozV6lCu57xpCgps8jTJuNKOcWE3iJxmDNBVH0-nnzXog.8s-4_87nfQ6JzT8vnx6VM4d_ecFHeAey6dSDKWjlYSkg.PNG/%EC%8B%B8%EB%B0%94%EB%A6%AC_%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8004.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F224007356427#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
